<main>
  <div class="hero-section">
    <div class="project-tag-row">
      <span class="tag">C / C++</span>
      <span class="tag">Raspberry Pi</span>
      <span class="tag">IoT</span>
      <span class="tag">Live Streaming</span>
      <span class="tag">Motion Detection</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Wireless<br><span>Surveillance Robot</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A remotely controlled robot capable of detecting motion and transmitting live video in real-time — built for security monitoring and surveillance applications.</p>
  </div>

  <img src="robot.jpg" alt="Wireless Surveillance Robot" class="project-img" onerror="this.style.display='none';document.getElementById('img-fallback-1').style.display='flex'">
  <div id="img-fallback-1" class="project-img-fallback" style="display:none">🤖</div>

  <div class="section-block">
    <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    <p>This project involved designing and building a wireless surveillance robot that can be remotely controlled to navigate spaces while simultaneously detecting motion and streaming live video back to the operator.</p>
    <p>The robot uses camera modules to capture real-time footage and wireless communication protocols to transmit the video feed. Motion detection algorithms trigger alerts when movement is detected in the monitored area, making it ideal for security applications.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section-block">
    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">📡</div>
        <h3>Live Video Streaming</h3>
        <p>Real-time video transmission using wireless communication modules to a remote operator.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Motion Detection</h3>
        <p>Automated motion detection using camera sensors with alert functionality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">🕹️</div>
        <h3>Remote Control</h3>
        <p>Wireless remote navigation allowing the robot to be controlled from a safe distance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Real-time Response</h3>
        <p>Low-latency communication for immediate response to operator commands.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-block">
    <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
    <div class="tech-row">
      <span class="tag">C Programming</span>
      <span class="tag">C++</span>
      <span class="tag">Raspberry Pi</span>
      <span class="tag">Camera Module</span>
      <span class="tag">Wi-Fi Module</span>
      <span class="tag">Python</span>
      <span class="tag">GPIO Control</span>
      <span class="tag">Motor Driver</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-block">
    <h2>What I Learned</h2>
    <div class="outcomes">
      <div class="outcome-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i><span>Hands-on experience with Raspberry Pi GPIO programming and hardware interfacing</span></div>
      <div class="outcome-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i><span>Real-time video streaming implementation using wireless protocols</span></div>
      <div class="outcome-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i><span>Integration of hardware components — motors, camera, and wireless modules</span></div>
      <div class="outcome-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i><span>Motion detection algorithms and image processing basics</span></div>
      <div class="outcome-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i><span>Power management and embedded system design for mobile robots</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-row">
    <a href="https://github.com/arunkumar7950" target="_blank" class="btn-primary"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i> View on GitHub</a>
    <a href="index.html" class="btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Portfolio</a>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-projects">
    <span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;align-self:center">Other Projects</span>
    <a href="project-accident.html" class="nav-proj-link">Accident Detection System <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
    <a href="project-ai.html" class="nav-proj-link">AI Tools Web App <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
